Titolo: F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch, shortened to F.I.S.T., is a Metroidvania video game developed by TiGames and published by Bilibili. It was released on PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 on September 7, 2021, followed by a Windows port on October 3, 2021. The game follows Rayton, an anthropomorphic rabbit and former ace pilot who, using a giant mechanical fist, rising up against the robotic Legion that has invaded Torch City in an effort to liberate it from its oppressors. The game received positive reviews from critics, citing its graphics, world and gameplay.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 75
